version_description:
Minor Bug fixes

What's new in 5.11:
A brand new, clear design which makes it easier for you to find the news & stories that matter
This brand new version features live updates, faster loading, better navigation, offline reading and more stories than before.
We have listened to your feedback and completely rebuilt the Evening Standard app, focusing on stability and performance.

• Improved download speed
• Ability to double tap editions to zoom in/out
